    <name>removing-unclassified-memberships</name>
    <documentation>
        Two account types:

         - account/default
         - account/admin

        Three entitlement types:

         - entitlement/ad-group
         - entitlement/app-group
         - entitlement/admin-group

        Three associations:

         - adGroup: account/default vs entitlement/ad-group (tolerant = true)
         - appGroup: account/default vs entitlement/app-group (tolerant = true)
         - adminGroup: account/admin vs entitlement/admin-group (tolerant = false)

        The goal is to automatically remove all admin groups from default accounts.
        The problem is that these memberships do not fall into any association; they are present in ri:group attribute only.
        So, we mark this attribute as tolerant=false.

        See MID-10285.
    </documentation>
